如封咗佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"屌老母屯門公園果陣有冇周過 d 大媽呀"},{"pid":"58ec6dbe926277d0e635d686d54dd6b7d82edeb1","tid":2506743,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"小題大做"},{"pid":"c8c8a2bf73cdeb263abfb31a74554cac51f8e3e4","tid":2506743,"uid":362827,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:52:28.000Z","msg":"東方昇準備比懲教通櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a89b247c7c2d06a5d97097de551087e6a91496","tid":2506743,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfdd44f6776152b2f19b6fb1e20e97b3bc8f51b1","tid":2506743,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"一見到有小朋友去玩我就喝停佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"錯，報狗先正確"},{"pid":"0f8995c27a5453f94a822499548cb25d0c237ed7","tid":2506743,"uid":5588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:53:27.000Z","msg":"幾時告埋班小朋友父母疏忽照顧兒童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2881157adaa8f1ccb505352bd76bd30b48ea80","tid":2506743,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2518c3ea1f61bb33cb5c2a19f3f93a2a8413770b","tid":2506743,"uid":10504,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"發難渣wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得你貪就靜啦 <br />\n到時黨要查 你地全部打靶都似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"共產主義鐵拳都近架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b446ef16c4abd10bac3ad9303d07cf203fada3","tid":2506